746
01:00:11,970 --> 01:00:13,100
特惠旅馆
"Discount Inn."

747
01:00:25,850 --> 01:00:27,220
特惠旅馆

748
01:01:02,720 --> 01:01:05,280
女伴服务

749
01:01:07,460 --> 01:01:09,350
金发女郎，好
Yeah, OK. Blonde's fine.

750
01:01:11,900 --> 01:01:13,160
对了
Well, that's what they say.

751
01:01:14,030 --> 01:01:16,060
特惠旅馆，304号房间
The Discount Inn. 304.

752
01:01:17,100 --> 01:01:17,800
我叫莱纳
Leonard.

753
01:01:20,360 --> 01:01:21,380
想怎么样？
Well, what then?

754
01:01:21,690 --> 01:01:24,550
我们上床，你等我睡着
We just go to bed. You wait for me to fall asleep.

755
01:01:24,860 --> 01:01:26,490
然后上厕所，用力关门
You go into the bathroom and you slam the door.

756
01:01:26,860 --> 01:01:27,630
用力关门？
Slam it?

757
01:01:27,930 --> 01:01:29,090
用力到吵醒我
Yeah. Loud enough to wake me up.

758
01:01:29,370 --> 01:01:30,820
-只是这样吗？
-只是这样
-And that's it?
-That's it.

759
01:01:34,370 --> 01:01:36,760
先把这些东西四处放
yeah, first I just need you to put these things around the room.

760
01:01:40,380 --> 01:01:42,940
假装是你的东西、你的卧室
Just pretend they're your things and that this is your bedroom.

761
01:01:54,990 --> 01:01:55,820
要我穿上去吗？
Should I wear it?

762
01:01:56,060 --> 01:02:00,020
不用，就好像你刚刚脱下来
No, no, no. Uh, just like you took it off or something.

763
01:02:03,530 --> 01:02:05,590
我不要你用，对不起
I-I don't want you to use it. I'm sorry.

764
01:02:06,570 --> 01:02:09,100
只要你随便放在房里
Just... I just mean put them around the room, you know,

765
01:02:09,410 --> 01:02:11,670
就像是你的…你的东西
as if they were your... your things.

766
01:02:16,110 --> 01:02:17,640
你喜欢怎么样就怎么样好了
Whatever gets you off.

767
01:02:43,070 --> 01:02:44,960
我不怪警方不理会
I can't blame the cops for not taking me seriously.

768
01:02:45,280 --> 01:02:47,140
我的病不容易明白
This is difficult to understand.

769
01:02:47,480 --> 01:02:48,540
看看杰克斯・萨米吧
I mean, look at Sammy Jankis.

770
01:02:48,880 --> 01:02:50,040
杰克斯太太实在受不了
His own wife couldn't deal with it.

771
01:02:50,780 --> 01:02:52,840
怎么都不能让他恢复记忆
I told you about how she tried to get him to snap out of it.

772
01:02:53,280 --> 01:02:56,170
她终于来办公室见我
Eventually she came to see me at the office. I found out all kinds of shit.

773
01:02:56,950 --> 01:02:59,720
说用尽办法强逼萨米记忆
She told me about life with Sammy, how she treated him.

774
01:02:59,860 --> 01:03:01,010
谢谢你见我
Thank you for seeing me.

775
01:03:01,360 --> 01:03:02,380
甚至要萨米
It got to the point where she'd get Sammy

776
01:03:02,530 --> 01:03:03,890
把食物收藏起来
to hide food all around the house...

777
01:03:03,990 --> 01:03:05,690
要他记着收藏地点
and then she'd stop feeding him just to see if his hunger...

778
01:03:05,760 --> 01:03:07,790
否则就挨饿
would make him remember where he'd hidden the food.

779
01:03:10,170 --> 01:03:12,660
她不是狠心，只是希望萨米康复
She wasn't a cruel person. She just wanted old Sammy back.

780
01:03:13,040 --> 01:03:16,390
你认为萨米在假装
Mr. Shelby, you know all about Sammy and you've decided that he's faking.

781
01:03:16,670 --> 01:03:19,300
公司并没有说萨米假装
Mrs. Jankis, the company's position isn't that Sammy is faking anything.

782
01:03:19,580 --> 01:03:21,130
只是认为他的病不是…
It's just that his condition can't be shown to be...

783
01:03:21,450 --> 01:03:24,710
我只想知道你的真正看法
I just wanna know what your honest opinion about Sammy is.

784
01:03:25,080 --> 01:03:27,910
案件在上诉，我们不应该讨论
We shouldn't even be talking like this while the case is still open to appeal.

785
01:03:28,120 --> 01:03:29,580
我不会提出上诉
I'm not appealing the decision.

786
01:03:30,350 --> 01:03:31,150
那么你想怎么样？
Then why are you here?

787
01:03:31,420 --> 01:03:33,690
当我看到萨米
Try to understand. When I look at Sammy,

788
01:03:33,990 --> 01:03:37,080
我看的不是植物人
I don't see some... vegetable.

789
01:03:37,430 --> 01:03:39,160
而是以前的萨米
I see my same old Sammy.

790
01:03:41,600 --> 01:03:42,900
我总是抱有希望
What do you think that's like for me...

791
01:03:43,170 --> 01:03:45,930
总希望他完全是心理作祟
to suspect that he might be imagining this whole problem?

792
01:03:46,140 --> 01:03:48,030
总希望有办法…
And that if I just could say the right thing,

793
01:03:48,140 --> 01:03:50,930
让他痊愈
he'd snap out of it and go back to being normal.

794
01:03:52,580 --> 01:03:53,840
如果…
If I...

795
01:03:56,680 --> 01:04:00,470
萨米确实无可药救，那么…
If I knew that my old Sammy were truly gone,

796
01:04:00,650 --> 01:04:04,410
我会抛开过去，爱现在的萨米
then I could say good-bye and start loving this new Sammy.

797
01:04:06,860 --> 01:04:09,620
一天抱有希望，一天就死心不息
As long as I have doubt, I can't say good-bye and move on.

798
01:04:09,960 --> 01:04:11,090
你要我怎么样？
What do you want from me?

799
01:04:11,390 --> 01:04:14,520
我要你撇开公事半分钟
I want you to forget the company you work for for 30 seconds...

800
01:04:14,770 --> 01:04:18,600
告诉我萨米是不是假装
and tell me if you really believe that Sammy's faking his condition.

801
01:04:19,570 --> 01:04:20,760
我需要知道…
I need to know...

802
01:04:21,740 --> 01:04:23,400
你真正的想法
what you honestly believe.

803
01:04:28,680 --> 01:04:32,170
我相信萨米有记忆能力
I believe that Sammy should be physically capable of making new memories.

804
01:04:44,260 --> 01:04:45,190
我以为帮了她
I thought I helped her.

805
01:04:45,460 --> 01:04:47,020
以为她只是要一个答案
I thought she just needed some kind of answer.

806
01:04:47,400 --> 01:04:49,130
以为什么答案都不重要
I didn't think it was important what the answer was,

807
01:04:49,700 --> 01:04:50,700
“事实5：毒贩”

808
01:04:50,750 --> 01:04:52,060
以为她只要一个可信的答案
just that she had one to believe.

809
01:05:07,520 --> 01:05:08,970
这样好的车，你应该上锁
A car this nice you should lock.

810
01:05:09,250 --> 01:05:11,710
-你是谁！
-你的朋友泰迪
-Who the fuck are you?
-Teddy, your buddy.

811
01:05:11,990 --> 01:05:12,510
证明一下！
Prove it.

812
01:05:12,720 --> 01:05:15,520
你告诉过我萨米的事
Sammy. Remember Sammy? You told me about Sammy!

813
01:05:19,430 --> 01:05:20,920
你在我车内干什么？
What the fuck are you doing in my car?

814
01:05:21,200 --> 01:05:22,960
你连幽默感也忘掉？
What, your sense of humor went with the memory?

815
01:05:23,430 --> 01:05:25,030
你为什么在这里，知道吗？
Do you even know why you're here?

816
01:05:25,440 --> 01:05:26,270
有未了结的事
Unfinished business.

817
01:05:26,800 --> 01:05:27,430
莱尼
Lenny,

818
01:05:27,670 --> 01:05:31,460
告诉你吧，你的事已经了结
let me inform you. Your business here is very much finished.

819
01:05:31,710 --> 01:05:33,230
你为了娜塔莉娅，所以还在这里
You're still here because of Natalie.

820
01:05:33,510 --> 01:05:34,070
谁是娜塔莉娅？
Who's Natalie?

821
01:05:34,440 --> 01:05:36,970
傻瓜，你刚从谁的家走出来？
Schmuck, whose house do you think you just walked out of?

822
01:05:39,720 --> 01:05:41,640
对，看看照片吧
Oh, that's right. Take a look at your pictures.

823
01:05:41,990 --> 01:05:43,180
你肯定有她的照片
I bet you got one of her.

824
01:05:45,460 --> 01:05:47,340
拍得好啊，大摄影师
Oh, nice shot, Leibovitz.

825
01:05:48,460 --> 01:05:49,890
记下来吧
You'll wanna make a note.

826
01:05:50,460 --> 01:05:51,590
不要相信她
You can't trust her.

827
01:05:51,960 --> 01:05:52,620
为什么？
Oh, yeah? Why's that?

828
01:05:52,960 --> 01:05:56,060
因为她看出你有钱…
Because by now she's taken a look at this suit and the car...

829
01:05:56,470 --> 01:06:00,530
打算利用你，捞点油水
and she's starting to figure out ways of turning the situation to her advantage.

830
01:06:01,540 --> 01:06:04,130
她已经把你搭上手了
She's already got you staying with her, for Christ's sakes.

831
01:06:04,470 --> 01:06:05,500
你不可以回她的家
You can't go back in there.

832
01:06:05,780 --> 01:06:07,140
我介绍你入住间旅馆吧
Let me give you the name of a motel.

833
01:06:07,840 --> 01:06:10,440
碰到我，算你运气好
You're lucky I ran into you. That broad's bad news.

834
01:06:10,750 --> 01:06:11,870
那女的为什么碰不得？
What do you mean, "bad news"?

835
01:06:12,220 --> 01:06:13,340
她涉及毒品
She's involved with drugs.

836
01:06:14,180 --> 01:06:14,980
看到吗？
All right, look. These. You see these?

837
01:06:15,120 --> 01:06:16,240
费迪斯酒吧

838
01:06:16,720 --> 01:06:18,420
这是她服务的酒吧
This is the bar where she works.

839
01:06:18,760 --> 01:06:20,380
她的男朋友是毒贩
Her boyfriend's a drug dealer.

840
01:06:20,760 --> 01:06:23,120
她替他办事，传递消息
She takes orders for him, arranges meets.

841
01:06:23,490 --> 01:06:26,160
他把讯息写在纸的背后
He writes messages on the back of these.

842
01:06:26,500 --> 01:06:29,090
她趁斟酒时给他，偷偷替他传递
Then she slips him the answers when she serves him his drinks.

843
01:06:29,500 --> 01:06:30,190
关我什么事？
Why should I care?

844
01:06:30,800 --> 01:06:32,690
因为她惹上了麻烦…
Because when she gets jammed up,

845
01:06:33,370 --> 01:06:35,330
打算利用你来替她解决
she's gonna use you to protect herself.

846
01:06:35,640 --> 01:06:36,470
谁想找她的麻烦？
From who?

847
01:06:36,740 --> 01:06:39,370
想知道她男朋友下落的人
Guys are gonna wanna know what happened to her boyfriend.

848
01:06:39,610 --> 01:06:42,970
那人要找她出气．总有人受罪
Guys are gonna come after her. Somebody's gotta pay, Lenny.

849
01:06:43,350 --> 01:06:44,800
一定有人受罪
Somebody always pays.

850
01:06:45,020 --> 01:06:46,350
也许她想用你来挡灾
Maybe she'll make it you.

851
01:06:46,620 --> 01:06:48,540
-是吗？
-也许她想利用你来挡灾
-Oh, yeah?
-Well, maybe she'll make it you.

852
01:06:49,020 --> 01:06:49,680
是不是？
Is that it?

853
01:06:50,020 --> 01:06:51,720
你担心她利用我来对付你
You worried that she's gonna use me against you?

854
01:06:52,120 --> 01:06:53,490
为什么不会？
-No.
-Why not?

855
01:06:54,620 --> 01:06:56,850
因为她不认识我
Because she doesn't know who I am.

856
01:06:58,330 --> 01:07:00,850
-你为什么跟着我？
-也许我想帮你
-Why are you following me?
-Maybe I wanna help.

857
01:07:01,560 --> 01:07:03,950
她完全不知道你在调查什么
She doesn't know anything about your investigation,

858
01:07:04,370 --> 01:07:06,890
天才，记下来吧
okay, Einstein? So write this down.

859
01:07:07,600 --> 01:07:12,230
她提议帮你，其实是为了自已
When she offers to help, it'll be for her own reasons.

860
01:07:12,580 --> 01:07:17,170
我没有骗你，用我这支笔记下来
I'm not lying. Take my pen. Write this down.

861
01:07:17,550 --> 01:07:19,140
不要相信她
Do not trust her.

862
01:07:27,220 --> 01:07:28,750
现在高兴了没有？
There. You happy now?

863
01:07:29,060 --> 01:07:30,550
你离开本地我才高兴
I won't be happy until you leave town.

864
01:07:30,830 --> 01:07:31,780
为什么？
Why not?

865
01:07:32,400 --> 01:07:34,230
你留下来
You ever wonder how long you can hang around here

866
01:07:34,360 --> 01:07:36,090
迟早有人会问
before people start asking questions?

867
01:07:36,600 --> 01:07:37,220
问什么？
What sort of questions?

868
01:07:37,570 --> 01:07:39,300
问你自己应该问的问题
The same sort of questions you should be asking yourself.

869
01:07:39,600 --> 01:07:40,260
例如呢？
Like what?

870
01:07:40,600 --> 01:07:42,160
你为什么穿着名牌西服？开着名牌车？
Like, how did you get this suit, the car?

871
01:07:42,440 --> 01:07:43,670
-我有钱
-从哪里来？
-I have money.
-From what?

872
01:07:44,070 --> 01:07:44,730
我太太去世了
My wife's death.

873
01:07:45,340 --> 01:07:47,260
我以前在保险公司工作，所以买足了保险
I used to work in insurance. We were well covered.

874
01:07:49,350 --> 01:07:53,040
你痛失娇妻，于是去买美州豹？
So in your grief you wandered into a Jaguar dealership.

875
01:07:55,320 --> 01:07:56,880
回答不出来吧
You don't have a clue, do you?

876
01:07:57,650 --> 01:07:59,990
-你连自已是谁都不知道
-我知道
-You don't even know who you are.
-Yes, I do.

877
01:08:00,360 --> 01:08:01,580
我没有失忆
I don't have amnesia.

878
01:08:02,090 --> 01:08:04,050
意外前的事我统统记得
I remember everything right up until the incident.

879
01:08:04,330 --> 01:08:06,020
我叫莱纳・谢尔比，旧金山人
I am Leonard Shelby. I am from San Francisco...

880
01:08:06,300 --> 01:08:07,820
那是以前的身份
That's who you were.

881
01:08:08,160 --> 01:08:10,220
你不知道现在的身份
You do not know who you are,

882
01:08:10,630 --> 01:08:12,190
意外发生后…
what you've become since...

883
01:08:12,940 --> 01:08:14,060
你变成怎么样的人
the incident.

884
01:08:14,770 --> 01:08:16,660
你到处扮侦探
You wander around playing detective.

885
01:08:16,940 --> 01:08:19,670
连扮了多久都不知道
You don't even know how long ago it was.

886
01:08:21,110 --> 01:08:22,270
让我问问你
Let me put it this way.

887
01:08:22,750 --> 01:08:25,640
你推销保险，够钱穿名牌西装
Were you wearing designer suits when you sold insurance?

888
01:08:25,950 --> 01:08:28,010
-不是推销，是调查
-对
-I didn't sell insurance. I investigated it.
-Right.

889
01:08:28,080 --> 01:08:29,480
你是调查员
You're an investigator.

890
01:08:30,420 --> 01:08:32,510
你预先应该调查自已
Well, maybe you should start investigating yourself.

891
01:08:33,460 --> 01:08:34,910
谢谢你的忠告
Thank you for the advice.

892
01:08:37,390 --> 01:08:39,520
帮个忙，不要回到她家去
Look, do me a favor. Don't go back in there.

893
01:08:40,630 --> 01:08:42,360
住旅馆好不好？
Will you take the motel out of town?

894
01:08:46,340 --> 01:08:47,530
拜拜，莱尼
It's been fun, Lenny.

895
01:08:55,650 --> 01:08:56,770
不要相信她
"Do not trust her."

896
01:08:57,210 --> 01:08:58,610
“泰迪” “5550134”

897
01:08:59,150 --> 01:09:00,840
不要受他的骗
"Don't believe his lies."

898
01:09:12,930 --> 01:09:14,190
“特惠旅馆”

899
01:09:14,330 --> 01:09:16,060
算了，我自己租房住
Oh, fuck it. I need my own place.

900
01:09:20,040 --> 01:09:21,400
“特惠旅馆”

901
01:09:24,270 --> 01:09:26,610
杰克斯太太不应该逼我回答那种问题
No. She shouldn't have given me that responsibility.

902
01:09:27,280 --> 01:09:29,400
我是保险调查员，不是医生
I'm a claims investigator, not a doctor.

903
01:09:30,950 --> 01:09:33,250
对
Yeah, yeah. I guess.

904
01:09:33,680 --> 01:09:35,380
我有很多顾虑
But I've got all sorts of other considerations.

905
01:09:36,690 --> 01:09:39,250
法律责任、大笔的赔款…
Legal responsibility, large financ...

906
01:09:39,960 --> 01:09:42,410
“绝不要接听电话”

907
01:09:43,990 --> 01:09:44,790
谁？
Who is this?

908
01:09:57,510 --> 01:09:59,100
记下来，记下所发生的事情
Write this down. Write down what happened.

909
01:09:59,210 --> 01:10:02,570
记下来，集中精神，记着
Write it down. Write it down. Come on. Concentrate. Keep it in mind. Find a pen...

910
01:10:09,250 --> 01:10:10,150
什么事？
What happened?

911
01:10:10,490 --> 01:10:12,350
还用问？他打我
What does it look like? He beat the shit out of me.

912
01:10:12,520 --> 01:10:13,590
谁？
Who?

913
01:10:13,920 --> 01:10:14,920
谁？
Who?

914
01:10:15,730 --> 01:10:17,960
达德啊！达德打我
Fuck, Leonard. Dodd. Dodd beat the shit out of me.

915
01:10:18,260 --> 01:10:19,660
-为什么？
-为什么？都是你
-Why?
-Why? Because of you.

916
01:10:19,930 --> 01:10:21,690
我照你的吩咐，去找他
-Because I did what you told me to do!
-Calm down.

917
01:10:21,970 --> 01:10:24,420
告诉他泰迪的事，结果挨打！
Tell him about Teddy! Great fucking idea!

918
01:10:24,730 --> 01:10:26,530
冷静点
Calm down. Take it easy.

919
01:10:26,840 --> 01:10:27,770
不要怕
You're safe. It's okay.

920
01:10:29,770 --> 01:10:31,760
坐下来
Come on. Just sit down.

921
01:10:32,380 --> 01:10:33,210
坐
Sit down.

922
01:10:34,080 --> 01:10:35,310
坐
Here. Sit down.

923
01:10:37,250 --> 01:10:38,610
不要怕
Okay. You're okay.

924
01:10:39,250 --> 01:10:41,240
我拿些冰来给你敷脸
I'll just get some ice for your face.

925
01:10:56,870 --> 01:10:58,960
我按照你的吩咐去做
I did exactly what you told me to do.

926
01:11:00,340 --> 01:11:01,790
我去找达德
