01:23:10,600 --> 01:23:12,530
我替你换杯子
Let me, um, get you another one.

1112
01:23:13,370 --> 01:23:14,830
这个杯子有灰尘
I think this one's dusty.

1113
01:23:19,780 --> 01:23:21,540
-你为什么找我？
-要什么？
-Why are you calling me?
-What do you want?

1114
01:23:22,620 --> 01:23:23,670
我知道你是警察
I know you're a cop, but what do you want?

1115
01:23:23,750 --> 01:23:25,010
我犯了法？
Have I done something wrong?

1116
01:23:26,390 --> 01:23:27,880
做了坏事？
I don't know. Something bad, maybe.

1117
01:23:30,120 --> 01:23:32,490
为什么问我？我记不得
Why are you asking me? I can't remember what I've done.

1118
01:23:32,660 --> 01:23:33,880
你反正不会相信
You wouldn't believe me anyway.

1119
01:23:34,660 --> 01:23:37,150
你不会相信我有这种病
Because of my condition. You don't believe someone with this condition.

1120
01:23:37,730 --> 01:23:40,100
就像我不相信萨米一样！
Nobody believed Sammy! I didn't even fucking believe Sammy!

1121
01:23:41,400 --> 01:23:42,730
费迪斯酒吧
"Ferdy's Bar."

1122
01:23:45,640 --> 01:23:47,630
下班来，娜塔莉娅
"Come by after. Natalie."

1123
01:24:02,890 --> 01:24:03,950
啤酒，麻烦你
I'll have a beer, please.

1124
01:24:04,330 --> 01:24:06,160
-要什么？
-啤酒，麻烦你
-What do you want?
-A beer, please.

1125
01:24:06,260 --> 01:24:08,620
你穿成那模样来喝啤酒？
You can't just waltz in here dressed like that and ask for a beer.

1126
01:24:08,900 --> 01:24:10,920
-你们有服装规定？
-要什么？
-What, is there a dress code?
-Why are you here?

1127
01:24:11,230 --> 01:24:12,360
我想找个叫娜塔莉娅的人
I'm meeting someone called Natalie.

1128
01:24:12,800 --> 01:24:14,200
我就是
Well, that's me.

1129
01:24:14,540 --> 01:24:16,200
我们见过面，是不是？
Yeah. We met before, right?

1130
01:24:17,840 --> 01:24:18,670
那么我来做什么？
Then why am I here?

1131
01:24:18,940 --> 01:24:20,030
不知道，你自己说好了
I don't know. Tell me.

1132
01:24:20,240 --> 01:24:22,800
我记不得，我没有短期记忆
I don't remember. I have no short-term memory. It's not amnesia.

1133
01:24:22,880 --> 01:24:24,240
原来你是那个失忆的人
Oh, you're the memory guy.

1134
01:24:24,480 --> 01:24:25,740
你怎么知道？
How do you know about me?

1135
01:24:26,250 --> 01:24:27,840
我男朋友提过你
My boyfriend told me about you.

1136
01:24:28,180 --> 01:24:29,440
你男朋友叫什么？
Yeah? Who's your boyfriend?

1137
01:24:30,180 --> 01:24:31,740
杰米・格兰斯，认识吗？
Jimmy Grants. Do you know him?

1138
01:24:33,190 --> 01:24:33,920
不认识
No.

1139
01:24:34,720 --> 01:24:35,920
他认识你
Well, he knows you.

1140
01:24:36,690 --> 01:24:39,520
提到过你，说你住在特惠旅馆
He told me about you. He said you were staying at the Discount.

1141
01:24:40,190 --> 01:24:42,750
前不久有警察来找过你
In fact, a cop came by here earlier looking for you.

1142
01:24:43,500 --> 01:24:45,420
说要找一个…
Said he was looking for a guy who can't remember anything,

1143
01:24:45,470 --> 01:24:47,560
懵懵懂懂的人
wouldn't know how he got here or what he'd done.

1144
01:24:47,970 --> 01:24:49,770
说我这里很多这种人
Said I get a lot of guys around here like that.

1145
01:24:50,700 --> 01:24:53,800
酗酒是短期失忆的一个原因
Well, you know, chronic alcoholism is one cause of short-term memory loss.

1146
01:24:56,310 --> 01:24:57,270
你叫泰迪？
Are you Teddy?

1147
01:24:57,550 --> 01:24:58,840
不是，我叫莱纳
No. My name is Leonard.

1148
01:24:59,210 --> 01:25:01,410
-泰迪派你来？
-我不知道
-Did Teddy send you?
-I don't know.

1149
01:25:02,550 --> 01:25:03,780
杰米现在怎样了？
What's happened to Jimmy?

1150
01:25:04,320 --> 01:25:06,380
我也不知道，对不起
I don't know that either. Sorry.

1151
01:25:06,720 --> 01:25:07,680
你什么都记不得？
You don't remember anything?

1152
01:25:07,990 --> 01:25:10,790
记不得去过哪里、做过什么？
You don't remember where you've been or what you've just done.

1153
01:25:11,060 --> 01:25:13,120
记不得，我没有短期记忆
No. I can't make new memories.

1154
01:25:13,490 --> 01:25:14,890
什么都忘掉
Everything just fades.

1155
01:25:15,230 --> 01:25:16,360
那么你来做什么？
Then why did you come here?

1156
01:25:16,730 --> 01:25:17,820
我在口袋里找到这个
I found this in my pocket.

1157
01:25:21,040 --> 01:25:22,400
你的口袋？
Your pocket.

1158
01:25:47,600 --> 01:25:50,660
酒吧赌注，有兴趣参加吗？
Bar bet. Care to contribute?

1159
01:25:51,000 --> 01:25:51,460
不用客气
No, thanks.

1160
01:25:51,770 --> 01:25:52,560
彩金好多
It's for a lot of money.

1161
01:25:53,270 --> 01:25:55,790
参加嘛，是慈善的
Come on. Proceeds are going to charity. Help me out.

1162
01:26:27,200 --> 01:26:28,000
免费
On the house.

1163
01:26:34,170 --> 01:26:36,560
谁也不相信我
It's completely fucked because nobody believes you.

1164
01:26:37,950 --> 01:26:40,570
脑部受损，连说话也没有人信
It's amazing what a little brain damage will do for your credibility.

1165
01:26:41,150 --> 01:26:43,810
我以前不信萨米，应该有此报应
I guess it's some kind of poetic justice for not believing Sammy.

1166
01:26:44,180 --> 01:26:45,950
患我这种病的人…
You know the truth about my condition, officer?

1167
01:26:46,990 --> 01:26:47,940
什么都不知道
You don't know anything.

1168
01:26:48,920 --> 01:26:50,650
生气生得莫名其妙
You feel angry, you don't know why.

1169
01:26:51,330 --> 01:26:53,890
内疚得莫名其妙
You feel guilty, you have no idea why.

1170
01:26:55,060 --> 01:26:57,790
无论什么，十分钟就忘掉
You could do anything and not have the faintest idea ten minutes later.

1171
01:26:58,100 --> 01:26:59,830
萨米的事…
Like Sammy. I could have done something like Sammy.

1172
01:27:00,670 --> 01:27:01,460
我有没有告诉你？
I didn't tell you...

1173
01:27:02,370 --> 01:27:03,830
萨米和他太太的事
what happened to Sammy and his wife?

1174
01:27:05,670 --> 01:27:07,300
她到我办公室见我
Well, she came to see me at my office.

1175
01:27:07,570 --> 01:27:08,970
我以为她在试探
I thought she was just trying to catch me off guard,

1176
01:27:09,010 --> 01:27:11,570
我没有对她说真心话
so I didn't tell her what I really thought, but I never said that he was faking,

1177
01:27:11,750 --> 01:27:13,800
只说他的病是心理上的，而不是生理的
just that his condition was mental, not physical.

1178
01:27:14,150 --> 01:27:17,140
她回家，替萨米做最后的测试
I found out later that she went home and gave Sammy his final exam.

1179
01:27:18,720 --> 01:27:19,480
萨米
Sammy?

1180
01:27:20,390 --> 01:27:21,380
到时间替我打针了
It's time for my shot.

1181
01:27:37,640 --> 01:27:39,230
她深信萨米爱她
She knew beyond a doubt that he loved her.

1182
01:27:40,670 --> 01:27:42,130
于是用这个测试办法
So she found a way to test him.

1183
01:27:55,190 --> 01:27:56,140
萨米
Sammy.

1184
01:27:57,590 --> 01:27:58,990
到时间替我打针了
It's time for my shot.

1185
01:28:09,400 --> 01:28:10,800
她以为可以拆穿他
She really thought she'd call his bluff.

1186
01:28:11,140 --> 01:28:12,040
打了
There you go.

1187
01:28:13,140 --> 01:28:16,740
否则，她不想再活下去
Or she just didn't wanna live with the things she put him through.

1188
01:28:27,290 --> 01:28:28,220
萨米
Sammy.

1189
01:28:30,190 --> 01:28:31,490
到时间替我打针了
It's time for my shot.

1190
01:28:38,300 --> 01:28:39,420
不会痛
It won't hurt.

1191
01:29:23,980 --> 01:29:25,670
她不省人事，接着就死了
She went into a coma and never recovered.

1192
01:29:26,810 --> 01:29:29,870
萨米不明白，也不能解释
Sammy couldn't understand or explain what happened.

1193
01:29:32,490 --> 01:29:33,920
从此长住疗养院
He's been in a home ever since.

1194
01:29:34,290 --> 01:29:35,950
连妻子去世也不知道
He doesn't even know that his wife's dead.

1195
01:29:36,820 --> 01:29:40,060
我看错了萨米，看错了他太太
I was wrong about Sammy, and I was wrong about his wife.

1196
01:29:40,330 --> 01:29:43,920
她不是为钱，只是想了解病情
She wasn't interested in the money. She just needed to understand his problem.

1197
01:29:44,630 --> 01:29:46,500
他对惯性没有反应
His brain didn't respond to conditioning.

1198
01:29:46,800 --> 01:29:47,930
可是他不是骗子
But he wasn't a con man.

1199
01:29:48,240 --> 01:29:51,330
她以为萨米没有变
And when she looked into his eyes, she thought he could be the same person.

1200
01:29:51,770 --> 01:29:54,070
我也以为萨米认得我
When I looked into his eyes, I thought I saw recognition.

1201
01:29:54,510 --> 01:29:55,810
我现在知道是假装的
Now I know. You fake it.

1202
01:29:56,340 --> 01:29:58,940
他假装认得人
If you're supposed to recognize somebody, you just pretend to.

1203
01:29:59,210 --> 01:30:01,240
也许是为了博取赞许
You bluff it to get a pat on the head from the doctors.

1204
01:30:02,250 --> 01:30:04,240
也许为了冒充正常
You bluff it to seem less of a freak.

1205
01:30:08,390 --> 01:30:09,410
什么毒贩？
What drug dealer?

1206
01:30:14,660 --> 01:30:17,890
“事实6：车牌 SG1371U”

1207
01:30:18,300 --> 01:30:19,930
“纹身店”

1208
01:30:20,530 --> 01:30:23,370
“事实6：车牌…”

1209
01:30:35,720 --> 01:30:36,910
莱尼，你好
Hey, Lenny, how you doing?

1210
01:30:37,220 --> 01:30:38,280
这是私人地方，出去！
It's private back here.

1211
01:30:38,620 --> 01:30:40,110
我们是认识的
It's okay. We know each other. Right, kid?

1212
01:30:40,450 --> 01:30:41,320
你怎么知道我在这里？
How did you know I was here?

1213
01:30:41,660 --> 01:30:43,890
你把美洲豹停在前面
Oh, the Jag is out front. You should have put it around back.

1214
01:30:44,160 --> 01:30:45,280
你还在这里做什么？
What are you still doing here?

1215
01:30:45,630 --> 01:30:47,180
北方有很多纹身店
There's plenty of tattoo parlors up north.

1216
01:30:47,560 --> 01:30:48,820
我想趁还没忘记
I just wanted to get something down...

1217
01:30:49,130 --> 01:30:50,060
纹下来
before it slipped my mind.

1218
01:30:50,330 --> 01:30:51,630
把车匙给我吧，我帮你开走
Then give me the keys. I'll move it for you.

1219
01:30:51,770 --> 01:30:53,290
-不要紧
-出去等吧
-It'll be all right for a minute.
-Wait out there.

1220
01:30:54,070 --> 01:30:54,860
唉
Oh, for Christ...

1221
01:30:55,200 --> 01:30:57,030
等一等我好吗？
Look, give me a minute. I gotta get something for you.

1222
01:31:01,110 --> 01:31:05,100
“事实6：车牌 SG1371U”
Fact six. Car license SG 137IU.

1223
01:31:11,590 --> 01:31:13,680
等一等，好不好？
Look. Wait a minute, will ya?

1224
01:31:17,120 --> 01:31:18,520
好，我要送你离开本地
All right, we gotta get you out of here.

1225
01:31:18,860 --> 01:31:19,850
为什么？
-Why?
-Aw, man.

1226
01:31:20,090 --> 01:31:22,250
多此一问，你要我说多少遍？
Come on, Leonard. How many times I gotta tell you?

1227
01:31:22,500 --> 01:31:24,150
你在这里已经不安全了
It's not safe for you to hang around here anymore.

1228
01:31:24,400 --> 01:31:24,960
为什么？
Why not?

1229
01:31:25,030 --> 01:31:26,700
警察在找你
Because that cop's looking for you.

1230
01:31:26,970 --> 01:31:32,160
我要给你弄个新身份、新衣服
暂时换辆汽车，穿上去！
Now, I gotta get you a new identity, some new clothes. A different car would do for now. So put these on.

1231
01:31:32,240 --> 01:31:33,600
什么警察？
Whoa, whoa. What cop?

1232
01:31:34,910 --> 01:31:38,110
一个坏警察，他介绍你住特惠旅馆
He's a bad cop. He's the one who checked you into the Discount Inn.

1233
01:31:38,380 --> 01:31:39,400
他找了你已经好几天了
He's been calling you for days,

1234
01:31:39,610 --> 01:31:41,770
蒙骗你，把信封塞进你门底下
telling you shit, slipping envelopes under your door.

1235
01:31:41,950 --> 01:31:42,640
你怎知道？
How do you know this?

1236
01:31:42,880 --> 01:31:45,780
他告诉我，以为好笑，他在玩你
He told me. He thinks it's funny. He's been laughing at you.

1237
01:31:46,150 --> 01:31:46,640
你胡说
You're full of shit.

1238
01:31:46,920 --> 01:31:49,650
不是，他知道你不爱讲电话…
I'm not. He knows you're no good on the phone, so he's been calling you up.

1239
01:31:49,960 --> 01:31:51,020
所以找上门
Sometimes you don't answer the phone,

1240
01:31:51,360 --> 01:31:54,210
塞信封进你门里，吓到你听电话
so he slips shit under your door to scare you into answering the phone again,

1241
01:31:54,480 --> 01:31:57,360
骗你说约翰・G是毒贩
giving you a line of crap about John G. Being some local drug dealer.

1242
01:31:57,630 --> 01:31:58,600
杰米・格兰斯
Jimmy Grants.

1243
01:31:59,800 --> 01:32:00,630
谁是杰米・格兰斯？
Who's Jimmy Grants?

1244
01:32:00,900 --> 01:32:02,930
杰米是毒贩
Leonard, Jimmy's the drug dealer.

1245
01:32:03,200 --> 01:32:05,300
警察在调查他
The cop wants to know how his operation's run.

1246
01:32:05,440 --> 01:32:07,600
无论如何，你牵涉进去了
He's got some score in mind. Somehow you're involved.

1247
01:32:08,210 --> 01:32:09,300
你怎么认识他的？
How do you know him?

1248
01:32:10,010 --> 01:32:12,810
我是线人，他是外地警察
I'm a snitch. He's a cop from out of town.

1249
01:32:12,950 --> 01:32:14,310
于是走在一起
The local boys put us together.

1250
01:32:14,750 --> 01:32:16,880
假如他知道我帮你，一定会宰了我
If he knew I was helping you, he'd fucking kill me.

1251
01:32:17,180 --> 01:32:19,570
换上这些衣服吧
So take these clothes, put them on

1252
01:32:19,750 --> 01:32:21,150
然后快点离开本地
and get the fuck out of here.

1253
01:32:21,660 --> 01:32:23,180
莱纳，快走吧
Come on, Leonard. Just go.

1254
01:32:37,040 --> 01:32:39,430
“泰迪” “555O134”

1255
01:32:40,870 --> 01:32:43,100
“不要受他骗”

1256
01:32:44,540 --> 01:32:45,530
你胡说
You are full of shit.

1257
01:32:48,250 --> 01:32:50,270
下班后来找娜塔莉娅
"Come by after. Natalie."

1258
01:32:50,680 --> 01:32:51,620
费迪斯酒吧
"Ferdy's Bar."

1259
01:33:25,590 --> 01:33:26,680
“费迪斯酒吧”

1260
01:33:34,860 --> 01:33:35,660
杰米
Hey, Jimmy.

1261
01:33:39,000 --> 01:33:42,960
对不起，我…我认错了人
I'm sorry. I, uh, thought you were somebody else. Sorry.

1262
01:33:44,740 --> 01:33:45,640
不要紧
That's okay.

1263
01:33:54,750 --> 01:33:56,200
“下班后来找娜塔莉娅”

1264
01:34:00,050 --> 01:34:03,050
杰米・格兰斯在女友的酒吧贩毒？
So this Jimmy Grants deals drugs out of the bar where his girlfriend works?

1265
01:34:04,260 --> 01:34:06,420
他不会带她来，会自己来吧？
But he's not gonna bring her along. He'll come by himself, right?

1266
01:34:07,860 --> 01:34:10,230
最好以贩毒罪名指控他
I always figured the drugs angle would be the best way to get him.

1267
01:34:11,870 --> 01:34:14,890
探长，我随时都准备好
No, officer. I'm as ready as I'll ever be.

1268
01:34:15,900 --> 01:34:16,830
你来到了旅馆正门？
You're in the lobby?

1269
01:34:17,840 --> 01:34:18,630
你是什么样子？
What do you look like?

1270
01:34:19,840 --> 01:34:20,670
我马上出去
I'll be right there.

1271
01:35:03,980 --> 01:35:04,850
莱尼
Lenny.

1272
01:35:08,160 --> 01:35:09,180
你是盖玛探长？
Officer Gammell.

1273
01:35:12,030 --> 01:35:13,820
对，来吧
Yeah. Come on.

1274
01:35:30,640 --> 01:35:31,300
笑一笑
Hey, smile.

1275
01:35:31,580 --> 01:35:33,210
不要…不要在这里
Oh, don't... Not here.

1276
01:35:34,510 --> 01:35:35,170
这里拍吧
Over here.

1277
01:35:41,890 --> 01:35:44,120
是探长还是盖玛探员？
Now, is it Officer or Lieutenant Gammell?

1278
01:35:44,160 --> 01:35:46,690
这样，不要写姓盖玛，写泰迪好了
You know what? Don't write Gammell, just Teddy.

1279
01:35:47,460 --> 01:35:48,050
为什么？
Why?

1280
01:35:48,260 --> 01:35:49,320
我正在做卧底
I'm undercover.

1281
01:35:52,600 --> 01:35:54,520
他会经过
This is the directions where he's going.

1282
01:35:55,140 --> 01:35:56,590
我的电话在下面
My number's on the bottom if you need me.

1283
01:35:56,870 --> 01:35:57,600
你不来？
You're not coming?

1284
01:35:58,240 --> 01:35:59,930
不来，不方便去
No. It wouldn't be appropriate.

1285
01:36:04,950 --> 01:36:07,510
拍得不错，拍得我瘦了些
Nice picture. I look thin.

1286
01:36:11,380 --> 01:36:12,210
莱尼
Hey, Lenny.

1287
01:36:13,590 --> 01:36:14,490
好好修理他
Make him beg.

1288
01:37:46,850 --> 01:37:47,780
泰迪
Teddy!

1289
01:37:50,820 --> 01:37:51,680
杰米？
Jimmy.

1290
01:37:53,750 --> 01:37:54,710
你在这里做什么？
